# MDX Blog Posts

When using `<Icon name="..." />` in blog posts, the icon **must** be registered in `src/components/Blog/MdxComponents.tsx`. Unregistered names render nothing silently.

If you use a new icon name, add it to `MdxComponents.tsx`:
1. Import the Lucide component (e.g. `import { Star } from 'lucide-react'`)
2. Add an entry to `iconMap` (e.g. `star: Star`)

Reference existing blog posts in `src/markdown/blog/` for frontmatter format, component usage, and style conventions.
